casebody.data:
Friday, November 17, 1995

MOTION DOCKET

95-953. White v. Clinton Cty. Bd. of Commrs.

Clinton County, No. CA94-08-020. On November 13,1995, appellees filed a merit brief and supplement to the brief which were due November 9,1995. S.CtJPrac.R. XIV(1)(C) prohibits the filing of a document that is not timely tendered for filing. Accordingly,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, effective November 15,1995, that appellees’ merit brief and supplement to the brief be, and hereby are, stricken.

Wright, J., not participating.
